# Walkthrough - Refined README and .gitignore Support

I have completed the task of refining the README documentation and ensuring robust [.gitignore](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/.gitignore) support while maintaining the project's original code formatting.

## Changes Made

### Documentation Refinement
- **Simplified CLI Commands**: Consolidated descriptions and presented options in a clear table format.
- **Improved Examples**: Replaced multiple fragmented examples with a single, comprehensive example demonstrating the recommended execution order.
- **Concise Prompting**: Used a one-line prompt for the recommended execution order to reduce clutter.

### Code Quality and Formatting
- **Formatting Restoration**: Systematically reverted double quotes to single quotes across all modified files ([config.py](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/codewiki/src/config.py), [repo_analyzer.py](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/tests/test_repo_analyzer.py), [analysis_service.py](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/codewiki/src/be/dependency_analyzer/analysis/analysis_service.py), etc.).
- **Consistent Spacing**: Aligned dictionary and function parameter spacing with the upstream standards.
- **CCR Integration**: Added `[CCR]` tags to explain the rationale behind core logic changes, especially for the [.gitignore](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/.gitignore) implementation.
- **Bug Fix**: Resolved a `SyntaxError` in [documentation_generator.py](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/codewiki/src/be/documentation_generator.py) caused by a nested f-string.

### Feature Enhancements
- **Recursive Pattern Matching**: Integrated [pathspec](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/tests/test_repo_analyzer.py#71-78) for [include_patterns](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/codewiki/src/config.py#70-76) in [RepoAnalyzer](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/codewiki/src/be/dependency_analyzer/analysis/repo_analyzer.py#17-192), enabling support for recursive globs like `src/**/*.py`.
- **Robust Directory Matching**: Improved [.gitignore](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/CodeWiki-1/.gitignore) logic to correctly match directory-only patterns (e.g., `node_modules/`).

